529
00:45:33,730 --> 00:45:35,690
Užijte si mandarinky.

530
00:46:02,670 --> 00:46:05,790
Odkud jdete?

531
00:46:05,790 --> 00:46:12,060
Co to bylo... to bylo.. ti lidé.

532
00:46:12,060 --> 00:46:14,850
Dok Mi!

533
00:46:26,720 --> 00:46:31,330
